data.description:
NEW CONSTRUCTION RANCH. Builder Short Sale. Time to Choose Selections. Two Bedrooms and Two Baths. 1,533 sq. ft. basement with 3 piece prep for bathroom and egress window. Cathedral Ceilings, Open Floor Plan and First Floor Laundry. Two Car Garage. Clubhouse Community with Pool, Hot Tub, Fitness Center, Tennis Court and Walking Trails. Connected to Lyon Trail System to Kensington Metro Park.

Brokered And Advertised By: PALAZZOLO BROTHERS CLASSICAL
Listing Agent: SAM PALAZZOLO
